<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="361" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,442,683]" pageId="7" pageNumber="361">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,586,611]" pageId="7" pageNumber="361">Diagnosis ♂.</emphasis>
Antennae black, except for the anterior and inner surface of the scape, white. Frontoclypeus almost entirely black. Mesoscutellum with four white markings. Metascutellum black. FW predominantly black, with various white spots. HW partially hyaline. T 
<number box="[707,720,659,683]" pageId="7" pageNumber="361" value="8.0">8</number>
black.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/265000/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="361" targetBox="[151,1436,735,1557]" targetPageId="7">
